# M3U Auto Updater Bot

![Python Version](https://img.shields.io/badge/python-3.7%20%7C%203.8%20%7C%203.9-blue)
![License](https://img.shields.io/badge/license-MIT-green)

This Python script is designed to automatically update M3U playlists. It fetches new data from specified sources, updates the M3U file, and can be scheduled to run periodically using cron or other scheduling tools.

## Features

- **Automatic Updating:** Fetches updated playlist data from sources.
- **Customizable Sources:** Easily configure sources of M3U data.
- **Logging:** Detailed logging of updates and errors.
- **Scheduled Execution:** Can be integrated with cron jobs or task scheduler for regular updates.

## Installation

### Prerequisites

- Python 3.7 or higher
- Required Python packages can be installed using pip:

  ```bash
  pip install -r requirements.txt
